<div class="com-share" data-id="26179" data-title="《宝洁今年发布的奥运广告，估计能感动很多人》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/26179/medium/26179.jpg?1461825630" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/26179.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
